Package: ampliSeqR
Title: Accelerated 16S Amplicon Sequencing Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Scott", "Developer", , "scott@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A package for efficient analysis of 16S amplicon sequencing data with
    hardware acceleration. Provides functions for file organization, quality control,
    sequence processing, ASV table generation, and visualization of results.
